Ideal module for LFS shop

Instructions:

* Install LFS
* Move the ideal directory into your project directory
* Include it in the INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py
* Generate the needed certificates and put them in the /includes/ directory (see www.paydeal.nl)
* Run the apply_patch.sh (currently working with version 0.6.0b5
* Modify the templates if needed, currently in Dutch only

Good luck!
